Lead underwriters PaineWebber Group Inc&lt;PWJ> and Ryan, Beck and Co Inc &lt;RBCO> said an initial publicoffering of 537,500 shares of Montclair Savings Bank commonstock is under way at 15 dlrs per share.    Underwriters have been granted an option to purchase up toan additional 322,500 shares to cover overallotments.    The company also sold 1,612,500 shares in a subscriptionand community offering. Reuter&#3;